ry proposing to Theresa Nist, and the two got married in a televised special. Unfortunately, Gerry and Theresa \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/news/the-golden-bachelor-divorce-gerry-turner-theresa-nist-break-up-video-1235199648/\"\u003esplit up\u003c/a\u003e after just three months of marriage. A premiere date for Season 2 will be announced at a later date.   \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBachelor Nation, will you be tuning in to see if Mel gets a second chance at love? Give us your thoughts in a comment below.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
